  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个事件溯源架构的时序图，核心流程是：Aggregate产生事件后先存入Event Store，然后有个Reactor组件负责把事件转成异步任务推到Queue里，最后Queue Worker来消费并执行Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我梳理一下参与者顺序：Aggregate → Event Store → Reactor → Queue → Queue Worker → Side Effect。Reactor和Queue Worker是两个不同的worker角色对吗？Reactor只做推送，Queue Worker做实际执行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue Worker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Reactor是反应式的，收到事件就Push Job到Queue；Queue Worker是轮询的，从Queue里Process Job。另外Side Effect执行完要有分支逻辑——成功就Mark Completed，失败要Retry。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Retry"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主链路：Aggregate调用Store Event到Event Store，Event Store Dispatch Event给Reactor，Reactor Push Job到Queue，Queue Worker Process Job，最后Execute Side Effect。分支用alt/else来处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event",
        "Push Job",
        "Process Job",
        "Execute Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Store Event的方向确认一下，是Aggregate指向Event Store对吧？还有Dispatch Event也是Event Store主动推给Reactor？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，都是单向箭头：A到E是Store Event，E到R是Dispatch Event。分支细节我这样画——Success时Side Effect返回给Queue Worker，然后Worker标记Job完成；Failure时返回Failure并触发Retry。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Return Success",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Return Failure",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Mark Job as Completed和Retry Job的返回对象应该是Queue，不是Queue Worker自己。Worker操作完要更新Queue里的任务状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，W到Q画两条返回：Mark Job as Completed和Retry Job。整个流程闭环了——从Aggregate产生事件，到最终Side Effect执行结果反馈回Queue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
